The company was named “Real Estate Agency Brand of the Year” and was recently awarded Top Workplaces in 2022.  With over 5000 sales professionals in more than 75 sales offices across the Tri-State area, the company was recently acknowledged as #1, for the seventh year in a row, in the entire national Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Network. Through its affiliated services, the Trident Group and Prosperity Home Mortgage, LLC; the company provides one-stop shopping and facilitated services to its clients including mortgage financing, and title, property and casualty insurance. The company-sponsored charitable foundation, Fox & Roach/Trident Charities, is committed to addressing the needs of children and families in stressful life circumstances and has contributed over $8 million to more than 250 local organizations since its inception in 1995. Visit us at www.foxroach.com

data.description: Welcome to 1141 Clayton  Greenspring Road.  This spacious 3 bed/2.5 bath , nestled in a country serene location with beautiful trees for miles perched on your 1.59 acres is waiting for you .Once driving down those quiet roads with wide open fields on all sides, will make you say I don't want to leave.This charming home is brimming with potential and awaits your creative touch to bring it back to its full glory. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the generous living space, perfect for accommodating your vision of a dream home. The three bedrooms offer plenty of space for relaxation with the primary bedroom  having its own 1/2 bath. With your imagination and TLC, these rooms can be transformed into tranquil retreats, tailored to your personal style and preferences. While this property needs work, the potential is limitless. With your creative eye and a little investment, you can turn this home with good bones into a true gem. This property offers an excellent opportunity to make your mark and add value. Outside, you'll find plenty of spacious yard, perfect for gardening, outdoor activities, or even expanding the living space and, feel free to bring your horses or livestock . The possibilities are endless when it comes to creating an outdoor oasis that complements the beauty of the surrounding nature. This property offers a retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life while still being conveniently close to the amenities, schools, transportation. Don't miss out on this chance to invest in a property with great potential. Bring your vision and transform this spacious three-bedroom home into a haven of comfort and style. Let your imagination run away with the possibilities that await! This Property is being Sold  in as is Condition Seller will make no repairs. 2023-12-10
